    - "No human role may disable JVL, RCG, or LEI=1 semantics."
    - "Policy changes must pass TQC/LTCC reasonability checks before activation."
  example_roles:
    - "Head of State / Sovereign Authority"
    - "National Security Council / Regulator"
    - "Supreme Judicial Entity for disputes"

